text: Jérôme Gay (born 9 February 1975) is a French ski jumper. He competed at the 1992 Winter Olympics and the 1998 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1975 births Category:Living people Category:French male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of France Category:Ski jumpers at the 1992 Winter Olympics Category:Ski jumpers at the 1998 Winter Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Haute-Savoie
